</head>
<body>
    <header class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <a href="/" class="logo"><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> AgriMind</a>
            <button class="mobile-menu-toggle" id="mobile-menu-toggle">
                <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
            </button>
          <ul class="nav-links" id="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                
                <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
                    <li id="dashboard-link"><a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/feedback">Feedback</a></li>
                <% } else { %>
                    <li id="dashboard-link" style="display:none;"><a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a></li>
                <% } %>
                
                <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/analytics">Analytics</a></li>
            </ul>
              <div class="auth-buttons">
                <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
                    <form action="/logout" method="POST" style="display: inline;">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary">Logout</button>
                    </form>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary" id="login-btn">Log In</a>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn" id="register-btn">Sign Up</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="page-content">
        <div class="page-header">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>About AgriMind</h1>
                <p>Empowering farmers with the power of data and artificial intelligence</p>
                <div class="header-decoration">
                    <div class="decoration-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-seedling"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="decoration-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="decoration-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <section class="about-section">
                <div class="section-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <h2>Problem Statement</h2>
                    <p>Farmers in India often rely on traditional farming practices, which can lead to suboptimal crop selection, lower yields, and financial instability. They face challenges in accessing accurate, localized information about which crops are best suited for their specific soil type, climate conditions, and market demand.</p>
                    <div class="problem-stats">
                        <div class="stat">
                            <h3>60%</h3>
                            <p>Farmers rely on traditional methods</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat">
                            <h3>40%</h3>
                            <p>Experience crop selection issues</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat">
                            <h3>30%</h3>
                            <p>Face financial instability</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="about-section">
                <div class="section-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>AgriMind aims to bridge this information gap by providing a simple, accessible, and data-driven tool. Our AI-powered recommendation engine analyzes various parameters—soil health, weather patterns, rainfall, and market prices—to suggest the most profitable and sustainable crops for farmers, helping them make informed decisions and improve their livelihoods.</p>
                    <div class="mission-features">
                        <div class="feature">
                            <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
                            <h4>AI-Powered</h4>
                            <p>Advanced algorithms for accurate recommendations</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature">
                            <i class="fas fa-database"></i>
                            <h4>Data-Driven</h4>
                            <p>Based on real-time soil and weather data</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature">
                            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                            <h4>Accessible</h4>
                            <p>Works on any device with internet</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="about-section">
                <div class="section-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <h2>Benefits for Farmers</h2>
                    <div class="benefits-grid">
                        <div class="benefit-card">
                            <div class="benefit-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3>Increased Profitability</h3>
                            <p>By selecting crops with high yield potential and market value, farmers can significantly increase their income and financial stability.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="benefit-card">
                            <div class="benefit-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3>Improved Sustainability</h3>
                            <p>Recommending crops that are well-suited to the local environment, reducing the need for excessive water, fertilizers, and pesticides.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="benefit-card">
                            <div class="benefit-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3>Risk Mitigation</h3>
                            <p>Helping farmers avoid crops that are likely to fail due to environmental factors, protecting their investments and livelihoods.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="benefit-card">
                            <div class="benefit-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3>Easy Access to Information</h3>
                            <p>A user-friendly platform available on any device, with multilingual support to ensure accessibility for all farmers.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="team-section">
                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                <p class="vision-text">We envision a future where every farmer in India has access to cutting-edge agricultural technology, enabling sustainable 
                    farming practices and prosperous rural communities.</p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

